# fields.prompt

**Fields for cdfooter**:
1. `selectableVariant` (string) - "default" or "xDemo"
2. `title` (string) - Footer Title
3. `subtitle` (string) - Optional subtitle
4. `logo` (image) - The footer logo
5. `links` (array of objects) - link label and URL
6. `sortOrder` (number)
7. `globalComponentSource` (reference) - optional global reusability